Note:
Mobile Media Components Module for Mobile UI Framework

This module provides comprehensive media display components for mobile interfaces.
Includes image views, video players, audio controls, and media galleries optimized
for mobile viewing with touch interactions and performance considerations.

Key Features:
- Responsive image views with scaling modes
- Video player with custom controls
- Audio player with waveform visualization
- Photo galleries with zoom and pan
- Media carousels and sliders
- Live photo and GIF support
- Picture-in-picture mode
- Media caching and lazy loading
- Thumbnail generation
- Media metadata display
- Full-screen viewing modes
- Social media integration

Provides complete media component system for building rich multimedia
mobile interfaces with optimal performance and user experience.
:End Note

